sec.p:
Following14,36, we define the conditional probability of having no further event between times t and s for a patient with distant relapse at time t as
SD(s,t|x)=exp⁡{−∫ts(λD,C(u|x)+λD,O(u|x))du}
where λi,j (t|x) is the hazard of moving from state i to state j at time t with the vector of covariates x (including the time from surgery or age, that must be updated after a relapse).
